id="secondary" class="layout__secondary" data-reactid="72"></div></div></div></div><script>(function() {
	function isSupported() {
		var ios, version, ua, android, matches;

		ua = window.navigator.userAgent;

		if ( ! window.history ||
				! window.history.pushState ||
				! window.history.replaceState ||
				! ( \'__proto__\' in Object.prototype )
		) {
			return false;
		}

		function getFirstMatch( regex ) {
			var match = ua.match( regex );
			return ( match && match.length > 1 && match[1] ) || \'\';
		}

		ios = getFirstMatch( /(ipod|iphone|ipad)/i ).toLowerCase();
		version = getFirstMatch( /version\\/(\\d+(\\.\\d+)? )/i );

		if ( ios && version < 6 ) {
			// disable for now because it is breaking Chrome on iOS
			//return false;
		}

		android = getFirstMatch( /android (\\d+)/i );
		if ( android && android < 3 ) {
			return false;
		}

		return true;
	}

	if ( ! isSupported() ) {
		if ( matches = window.location.pathname.match( /^\\/log-in(?:\\/([a-z]{2}))?\\/?$/ ) ) {
			var login = \'https://\'

			if ( matches[1] ) {
				login += matches[1] + \'.\';
			}

			login += \'wordpress.com/wp-login.php\';

			if ( window.location.search ) {
				login += window.location.search + \'&\';
			} else {
				login += \'?\';
			}
			login += \'no_calypso=1\';

			window.location = login;
		} else {
			window.location = \'https://wordpress.com/browsehappy?url=\' + encodeURIComponent( window.location );
		}
	}
})();

class="wp-login__footer wp-login__footer--jetpack" data-reactid="70"><img src="/calypso/images/jetpack/powered-by-jetpack.svg" alt="Powered by Jetpack" data-reactid="71"/></div></div></div><div id="secondary" class="layout__secondary" data-reactid="72"></div></div></div></div><script>(function() {
	function isSupported() {
		var ios, version, ua, android, matches;

		ua = window.navigator.userAgent;

		if ( ! window.history ||
				! window.history.pushState ||
				! window.history.replaceState ||
				! ( \'__proto__\' in Object.prototype )
		) {
			return false;
		}

		function getFirstMatch( regex ) {
			var match = ua.match( regex );
			return ( match && match.length > 1 && match[1] ) || \'\';
		}

		ios = getFirstMatch( /(ipod|iphone|ipad)/i ).toLowerCase();
		version = getFirstMatch( /version\\/(\\d+(\\.\\d+)? )/i );

		if ( ios && version < 6 ) {
			// disable for now because it is breaking Chrome on iOS
			//return false;
		}

		android = getFirstMatch( /android (\\d+)/i );
		if ( android && android < 3 ) {
			return false;
		}

		return true;
	}

	if ( ! isSupported() ) {
		if ( matches = window.location.pathname.match( /^\\/log-in(?:\\/([a-z]{2}))?\\/?$/ ) ) {
			var login = \'https://\'

			if ( matches[1] ) {
				login += matches[1] + \'.\';
			}

			login += \'wordpress.com/wp-login.php\';

			if ( window.location.search ) {
				login += window.location.search + \'&\';
			} else {
				login += \'?\';
			}
			login += \'no_calypso=1\';

			window.location = login;
		} else {
			window.location = \'https://wordpress.com/browsehappy?url=\' + encodeURIComponent( window.location );
		}
	}
})();

id="secondary" class="layout__secondary" data-reactid="72"></div></div></div></div><script>(function() {
	function isSupported() {
		var ios, version, ua, android, matches;

		ua = window.navigator.userAgent;

		if ( ! window.history ||
				! window.history.pushState ||
				! window.history.replaceState ||
				! ( \'__proto__\' in Object.prototype )
		) {
			return false;
		}

		function getFirstMatch( regex ) {
			var match = ua.match( regex );
			return ( match && match.length > 1 && match[1] ) || \'\';
		}

		ios = getFirstMatch( /(ipod|iphone|ipad)/i ).toLowerCase();
		version = getFirstMatch( /version\\/(\\d+(\\.\\d+)? )/i );

		if ( ios && version < 6 ) {
			// disable for now because it is breaking Chrome on iOS
			//return false;
		}

		android = getFirstMatch( /android (\\d+)/i );
		if ( android && android < 3 ) {
			return false;
		}

		return true;
	}

	if ( ! isSupported() ) {
		if ( matches = window.location.pathname.match( /^\\/log-in(?:\\/([a-z]{2}))?\\/?$/ ) ) {
			var login = \'https://\'

			if ( matches[1] ) {
				login += matches[1] + \'.\';
			}

			login += \'wordpress.com/wp-login.php\';

			if ( window.location.search ) {
				login += window.location.search + \'&\';
			} else {
				login += \'?\';
			}
			login += \'no_calypso=1\';

			window.location = login;
		} else {
			window.location = \'https://wordpress.com/browsehappy?url=\' + encodeURIComponent( window.location );
		}
	}
})();

id="secondary" class="layout__secondary" data-reactid="72"></div></div></div></div><script>(function() {
	function isSupported() {
		var ios, version, ua, android, matches;

		ua = window.navigator.userAgent;

		if ( ! window.history ||
				! window.history.pushState ||
				! window.history.replaceState ||
				! ( \'__proto__\' in Object.prototype )
		) {
			return false;
		}

		function getFirstMatch( regex ) {
			var match = ua.match( regex );
			return ( match && match.length > 1 && match[1] ) || \'\';
		}

		ios = getFirstMatch( /(ipod|iphone|ipad)/i ).toLowerCase();
		version = getFirstMatch( /version\\/(\\d+(\\.\\d+)? )/i );

		if ( ios && version < 6 ) {
			// disable for now because it is breaking Chrome on iOS
			//return false;
		}

		android = getFirstMatch( /android (\\d+)/i );
		if ( android && android < 3 ) {
			return false;
		}

		return true;
	}

	if ( ! isSupported() ) {
		if ( matches = window.location.pathname.match( /^\\/log-in(?:\\/([a-z]{2}))?\\/?$/ ) ) {
			var login = \'https://\'

			if ( matches[1] ) {
				login += matches[1] + \'.\';
			}

			login += \'wordpress.com/wp-login.php\';

			if ( window.location.search ) {
				login += window.location.search + \'&\';
			} else {
				login += \'?\';
			}
			login += \'no_calypso=1\';

			window.location = login;
		} else {
			window.location = \'https://wordpress.com/browsehappy?url=\' + encodeURIComponent( window.location );
		}
	}
})();

	function isSupported() {
		var ios, version, ua, android, matches;

		ua = window.navigator.userAgent;

		if ( ! window.history ||
				! window.history.pushState ||
				! window.history.replaceState ||
				! ( \'__proto__\' in Object.prototype )
		) {
			return false;
		}

		function getFirstMatch( regex ) {
			var match = ua.match( regex );
			return ( match && match.length > 1 && match[1] ) || \'\';
		}

		ios = getFirstMatch( /(ipod|iphone|ipad)/i ).toLowerCase();
		version = getFirstMatch( /version\\/(\\d+(\\.\\d+)? )/i );

		if ( ios && version < 6 ) {
			// disable for now because it is breaking Chrome on iOS
			//return false;
		}

		android = getFirstMatch( /android (\\d+)/i );
		if ( android && android < 3 ) {
			return false;
		}

		return true;
	}

	if ( ! isSupported() ) {
		if ( matches = window.location.pathname.match( /^\\/log-in(?:\\/([a-z]{2}))?\\/?$/ ) ) {
			var login = \'https://\'

			if ( matches[1] ) {
				login += matches[1] + \'.\';
			}

			login += \'wordpress.com/wp-login.php\';

			if ( window.location.search ) {
				login += window.location.search + \'&\';
			} else {
				login += \'?\';
			}
			login += \'no_calypso=1\';

			window.location = login;
		} else {
			window.location = \'https://wordpress.com/browsehappy?url=\' + encodeURIComponent( window.location );
		}
	}
})();

id="secondary" class="layout__secondary" data-reactid="72"></div></div></div></div><script>(function() {
	function isSupported() {
		var ios, version, ua, android, matches;

		ua = window.navigator.userAgent;

		if ( ! window.history ||
				! window.history.pushState ||
				! window.history.replaceState ||
				! ( '__proto__' in Object.prototype )
		) {
			return false;
		}

		function getFirstMatch( regex ) {
			var match = ua.match( regex );
			return ( match && match.length > 1 && match[1] ) || '';
		}

		ios = getFirstMatch( /(ipod|iphone|ipad)/i ).toLowerCase();
		version = getFirstMatch( /version\/(\d+(\.\d+)? )/i );

		if ( ios && version < 6 ) {
			// disable for now because it is breaking Chrome on iOS
			//return false;
		}

		android = getFirstMatch( /android (\d+)/i );
		if ( android && android < 3 ) {
			return false;
		}

		return true;
	}

	if ( ! isSupported() ) {
		if ( matches = window.location.pathname.match( /^\/log-in(?:\/([a-z]{2}))?\/?$/ ) ) {
			var login = 'https://'

			if ( matches[1] ) {
				login += matches[1] + '.';
			}

			login += 'wordpress.com/wp-login.php';

			if ( window.location.search ) {
				login += window.location.search + '&';
			} else {
				login += '?';
			}
			login += 'no_calypso=1';

			window.location = login;
		} else {
			window.location = 'https://wordpress.com/browsehappy?url=' + encodeURIComponent( window.location );
		}
	}
})();

	function isSupported() {
		var ios, version, ua, android, matches;

		ua = window.navigator.userAgent;

		if ( ! window.history ||
				! window.history.pushState ||
				! window.history.replaceState ||
				! ( \'__proto__\' in Object.prototype )
		) {
			return false;
		}

		function getFirstMatch( regex ) {
			var match = ua.match( regex );
			return ( match && match.length > 1 && match[1] ) || \'\';
		}

		ios = getFirstMatch( /(ipod|iphone|ipad)/i ).toLowerCase();
		version = getFirstMatch( /version\\/(\\d+(\\.\\d+)? )/i );

		if ( ios && version < 6 ) {
			// disable for now because it is breaking Chrome on iOS
			//return false;
		}

		android = getFirstMatch( /android (\\d+)/i );
		if ( android && android < 3 ) {
			return false;
		}

		return true;
	}

	if ( ! isSupported() ) {
		if ( matches = window.location.pathname.match( /^\\/log-in(?:\\/([a-z]{2}))?\\/?$/ ) ) {
			var login = \'https://\'

			if ( matches[1] ) {
				login += matches[1] + \'.\';
			}

			login += \'wordpress.com/wp-login.php\';

			if ( window.location.search ) {
				login += window.location.search + \'&\';
			} else {
				login += \'?\';
			}
			login += \'no_calypso=1\';

			window.location = login;
		} else {
			window.location = \'https://wordpress.com/browsehappy?url=\' + encodeURIComponent( window.location );
		}
	}
})();

	function isSupported() {
		var ios, version, ua, android, matches;

		ua = window.navigator.userAgent;

		if ( ! window.history ||
				! window.history.pushState ||
				! window.history.replaceState ||
				! ( \'__proto__\' in Object.prototype )
		) {
			return false;
		}

		function getFirstMatch( regex ) {
			var match = ua.match( regex );
			return ( match && match.length > 1 && match[1] ) || \'\';
		}

		ios = getFirstMatch( /(ipod|iphone|ipad)/i ).toLowerCase();
		version = getFirstMatch( /version\\/(\\d+(\\.\\d+)? )/i );

		if ( ios && version < 6 ) {
			// disable for now because it is breaking Chrome on iOS
			//return false;
		}

		android = getFirstMatch( /android (\\d+)/i );
		if ( android && android < 3 ) {
			return false;
		}

		return true;
	}

	if ( ! isSupported() ) {
		if ( matches = window.location.pathname.match( /^\\/log-in(?:\\/([a-z]{2}))?\\/?$/ ) ) {
			var login = \'https://\'

			if ( matches[1] ) {
				login += matches[1] + \'.\';
			}

			login += \'wordpress.com/wp-login.php\';

			if ( window.location.search ) {
				login += window.location.search + \'&\';
			} else {
				login += \'?\';
			}
			login += \'no_calypso=1\';

			window.location = login;
		} else {
			window.location = \'https://wordpress.com/browsehappy?url=\' + encodeURIComponent( window.location );
		}
	}
})();

	function isSupported() {
		var ios, version, ua, android, matches;

		ua = window.navigator.userAgent;

		if ( ! window.history ||
				! window.history.pushState ||
				! window.history.replaceState ||
				! ( \'__proto__\' in Object.prototype )
		) {
			return false;
		}

		function getFirstMatch( regex ) {
			var match = ua.match( regex );
			return ( match && match.length > 1 && match[1] ) || \'\';
		}

		ios = getFirstMatch( /(ipod|iphone|ipad)/i ).toLowerCase();
		version = getFirstMatch( /version\\/(\\d+(\\.\\d+)? )/i );

		if ( ios && version < 6 ) {
			// disable for now because it is breaking Chrome on iOS
			//return false;
		}

		android = getFirstMatch( /android (\\d+)/i );
		if ( android && android < 3 ) {
			return false;
		}

		return true;
	}

	if ( ! isSupported() ) {
		if ( matches = window.location.pathname.match( /^\\/log-in(?:\\/([a-z]{2}))?\\/?$/ ) ) {
			var login = \'https://\'

			if ( matches[1] ) {
				login += matches[1] + \'.\';
			}

			login += \'wordpress.com/wp-login.php\';

			if ( window.location.search ) {
				login += window.location.search + \'&\';
			} else {
				login += \'?\';
			}
			login += \'no_calypso=1\';

			window.location = login;
		} else {
			window.location = \'https://wordpress.com/browsehappy?url=\' + encodeURIComponent( window.location );
		}
	}
})();

	function isSupported() {
		var ios, version, ua, android, matches;

		ua = window.navigator.userAgent;

		if ( ! window.history ||
				! window.history.pushState ||
				! window.history.replaceState ||
				! ( \'__proto__\' in Object.prototype )
		) {
			return false;
		}

		function getFirstMatch( regex ) {
			var match = ua.match( regex );
			return ( match && match.length > 1 && match[1] ) || \'\';
		}

		ios = getFirstMatch( /(ipod|iphone|ipad)/i ).toLowerCase();
		version = getFirstMatch( /version\\/(\\d+(\\.\\d+)? )/i );

		if ( ios && version < 6 ) {
			// disable for now because it is breaking Chrome on iOS
			//return false;
		}

		android = getFirstMatch( /android (\\d+)/i );
		if ( android && android < 3 ) {
			return false;
		}

		return true;
	}

	if ( ! isSupported() ) {
		if ( matches = window.location.pathname.match( /^\\/log-in(?:\\/([a-z]{2}))?\\/?$/ ) ) {
			var login = \'https://\'

			if ( matches[1] ) {
				login += matches[1] + \'.\';
			}

			login += \'wordpress.com/wp-login.php\';

			if ( window.location.search ) {
				login += window.location.search + \'&\';
			} else {
				login += \'?\';
			}
			login += \'no_calypso=1\';

			window.location = login;
		} else {
			window.location = \'https://wordpress.com/browsehappy?url=\' + encodeURIComponent( window.location );
		}
	}
})();

id="secondary" class="layout__secondary" data-reactid="72"></div></div></div></div><script>(function() {
	function isSupported() {
		var ios, version, ua, android, matches;

		ua = window.navigator.userAgent;

		if ( ! window.history ||
				! window.history.pushState ||
				! window.history.replaceState ||
				! ( \'__proto__\' in Object.prototype )
		) {
			return false;
		}

		function getFirstMatch( regex ) {
			var match = ua.match( regex );
			return ( match && match.length > 1 && match[1] ) || \'\';
		}

		ios = getFirstMatch( /(ipod|iphone|ipad)/i ).toLowerCase();
		version = getFirstMatch( /version\\/(\\d+(\\.\\d+)? )/i );

		if ( ios && version < 6 ) {
			// disable for now because it is breaking Chrome on iOS
			//return false;
		}

		android = getFirstMatch( /android (\\d+)/i );
		if ( android && android < 3 ) {
			return false;
		}

		return true;
	}

	if ( ! isSupported() ) {
		if ( matches = window.location.pathname.match( /^\\/log-in(?:\\/([a-z]{2}))?\\/?$/ ) ) {
			var login = \'https://\'

			if ( matches[1] ) {
				login += matches[1] + \'.\';
			}

			login += \'wordpress.com/wp-login.php\';

			if ( window.location.search ) {
				login += window.location.search + \'&\';
			} else {
				login += \'?\';
			}
			login += \'no_calypso=1\';

			window.location = login;
		} else {
			window.location = \'https://wordpress.com/browsehappy?url=\' + encodeURIComponent( window.location );
		}
	}
})();

id="secondary" class="layout__secondary" data-reactid="72"></div></div></div></div><script>(function() {
	function isSupported() {
		var ios, version, ua, android, matches;

		ua = window.navigator.userAgent;

		if ( ! window.history ||
				! window.history.pushState ||
				! window.history.replaceState ||
				! ( '__proto__' in Object.prototype )
		) {
			return false;
		}

		function getFirstMatch( regex ) {
			var match = ua.match( regex );
			return ( match && match.length > 1 && match[1] ) || '';
		}

		ios = getFirstMatch( /(ipod|iphone|ipad)/i ).toLowerCase();
		version = getFirstMatch( /version\/(\d+(\.\d+)? )/i );

		if ( ios && version < 6 ) {
			// disable for now because it is breaking Chrome on iOS
			//return false;
		}

		android = getFirstMatch( /android (\d+)/i );
		if ( android && android < 3 ) {
			return false;
		}

		return true;
	}

	if ( ! isSupported() ) {
		if ( matches = window.location.pathname.match( /^\/log-in(?:\/([a-z]{2}))?\/?$/ ) ) {
			var login = 'https://'

			if ( matches[1] ) {
				login += matches[1] + '.';
			}

			login += 'wordpress.com/wp-login.php';

			if ( window.location.search ) {
				login += window.location.search + '&';
			} else {
				login += '?';
			}
			login += 'no_calypso=1';

			window.location = login;
		} else {
			window.location = 'https://wordpress.com/browsehappy?url=' + encodeURIComponent( window.location );
		}
	}
})();

id="secondary" class="layout__secondary" data-reactid="70"></div></div></div></div><script>(function() {
	function isSupported() {
		var ios, version, ua, android, matches;

		ua = window.navigator.userAgent;

		if ( ! window.history ||
				! window.history.pushState ||
				! window.history.replaceState ||
				! ( \'__proto__\' in Object.prototype )
		) {
			return false;
		}

		function getFirstMatch( regex ) {
			var match = ua.match( regex );
			return ( match && match.length > 1 && match[1] ) || \'\';
		}

		ios = getFirstMatch( /(ipod|iphone|ipad)/i ).toLowerCase();
		version = getFirstMatch( /version\\/(\\d+(\\.\\d+)? )/i );

		if ( ios && version < 6 ) {
			// disable for now because it is breaking Chrome on iOS
			//return false;
		}

		android = getFirstMatch( /android (\\d+)/i );
		if ( android && android < 3 ) {
			return false;
		}

		return true;
	}

	if ( ! isSupported() ) {
		if ( matches = window.location.pathname.match( /^\\/log-in(?:\\/([a-z]{2}))?\\/?$/ ) ) {
			var login = \'https://\'

			if ( matches[1] ) {
				login += matches[1] + \'.\';
			}

			login += \'wordpress.com/wp-login.php\';

			if ( window.location.search ) {
				login += window.location.search + \'&\';
			} else {
				login += \'?\';
			}
			login += \'no_calypso=1\';

			window.location = login;
		} else {
			window.location = \'https://wordpress.com/browsehappy?url=\' + encodeURIComponent( window.location );
		}
	}
})();

id="secondary" class="layout__secondary" data-reactid="70"></div></div></div></div><script>(function() {
	function isSupported() {
		var ios, version, ua, android, matches;

		ua = window.navigator.userAgent;

		if ( ! window.history ||
				! window.history.pushState ||
				! window.history.replaceState ||
				! ( \'__proto__\' in Object.prototype )
		) {
			return false;
		}

		function getFirstMatch( regex ) {
			var match = ua.match( regex );
			return ( match && match.length > 1 && match[1] ) || \'\';
		}

		ios = getFirstMatch( /(ipod|iphone|ipad)/i ).toLowerCase();
		version = getFirstMatch( /version\\/(\\d+(\\.\\d+)? )/i );

		if ( ios && version < 6 ) {
			// disable for now because it is breaking Chrome on iOS
			//return false;
		}

		android = getFirstMatch( /android (\\d+)/i );
		if ( android && android < 3 ) {
			return false;
		}

		return true;
	}

	if ( ! isSupported() ) {
		if ( matches = window.location.pathname.match( /^\\/log-in(?:\\/([a-z]{2}))?\\/?$/ ) ) {
			var login = \'https://\'

			if ( matches[1] ) {
				login += matches[1] + \'.\';
			}

			login += \'wordpress.com/wp-login.php\';

			if ( window.location.search ) {
				login += window.location.search + \'&\';
			} else {
				login += \'?\';
			}
			login += \'no_calypso=1\';

			window.location = login;
		} else {
			window.location = \'https://wordpress.com/browsehappy?url=\' + encodeURIComponent( window.location );
		}
	}
})();

id="secondary" class="layout__secondary" data-reactid="70"></div></div></div></div><script>(function() {
	function isSupported() {
		var ios, version, ua, android, matches;

		ua = window.navigator.userAgent;

		if ( ! window.history ||
				! window.history.pushState ||
				! window.history.replaceState ||
				! ( \'__proto__\' in Object.prototype )
		) {
			return false;
		}

		function getFirstMatch( regex ) {
			var match = ua.match( regex );
			return ( match && match.length > 1 && match[1] ) || \'\';
		}

		ios = getFirstMatch( /(ipod|iphone|ipad)/i ).toLowerCase();
		version = getFirstMatch( /version\\/(\\d+(\\.\\d+)? )/i );

		if ( ios && version < 6 ) {
			// disable for now because it is breaking Chrome on iOS
			//return false;
		}

		android = getFirstMatch( /android (\\d+)/i );
		if ( android && android < 3 ) {
			return false;
		}

		return true;
	}

	if ( ! isSupported() ) {
		if ( matches = window.location.pathname.match( /^\\/log-in(?:\\/([a-z]{2}))?\\/?$/ ) ) {
			var login = \'https://\'

			if ( matches[1] ) {
				login += matches[1] + \'.\';
			}

			login += \'wordpress.com/wp-login.php\';

			if ( window.location.search ) {
				login += window.location.search + \'&\';
			} else {
				login += \'?\';
			}
			login += \'no_calypso=1\';

			window.location = login;
		} else {
			window.location = \'https://wordpress.com/browsehappy?url=\' + encodeURIComponent( window.location );
		}
	}
})();

	function isSupported() {
		var ios, version, ua, android, matches;

		ua = window.navigator.userAgent;

		if ( ! window.history ||
				! window.history.pushState ||
				! window.history.replaceState ||
				! ( \'__proto__\' in Object.prototype )
		) {
			return false;
		}

		function getFirstMatch( regex ) {
			var match = ua.match( regex );
			return ( match && match.length > 1 && match[1] ) || \'\';
		}

		ios = getFirstMatch( /(ipod|iphone|ipad)/i ).toLowerCase();
		version = getFirstMatch( /version\\/(\\d+(\\.\\d+)? )/i );

		if ( ios && version < 6 ) {
			// disable for now because it is breaking Chrome on iOS
			//return false;
		}

		android = getFirstMatch( /android (\\d+)/i );
		if ( android && android < 3 ) {
			return false;
		}

		return true;
	}

	if ( ! isSupported() ) {
		if ( matches = window.location.pathname.match( /^\\/log-in(?:\\/([a-z]{2}))?\\/?$/ ) ) {
			var login = \'https://\'

			if ( matches[1] ) {
				login += matches[1] + \'.\';
			}

			login += \'wordpress.com/wp-login.php\';

			if ( window.location.search ) {
				login += window.location.search + \'&\';
			} else {
				login += \'?\';
			}
			login += \'no_calypso=1\';

			window.location = login;
		} else {
			window.location = \'https://wordpress.com/browsehappy?url=\' + encodeURIComponent( window.location );
		}
	}
})();

	function isSupported() {
		var ios, version, ua, android, matches;

		ua = window.navigator.userAgent;

		if ( ! window.history ||
				! window.history.pushState ||
				! window.history.replaceState ||
				! ( \'__proto__\' in Object.prototype )
		) {
			return false;
		}

		function getFirstMatch( regex ) {
			var match = ua.match( regex );
			return ( match && match.length > 1 && match[1] ) || \'\';
		}

		ios = getFirstMatch( /(ipod|iphone|ipad)/i ).toLowerCase();
		version = getFirstMatch( /version\\/(\\d+(\\.\\d+)? )/i );

		if ( ios && version < 6 ) {
			// disable for now because it is breaking Chrome on iOS
			//return false;
		}

		android = getFirstMatch( /android (\\d+)/i );
		if ( android && android < 3 ) {
			return false;
		}

		return true;
	}

	if ( ! isSupported() ) {
		if ( matches = window.location.pathname.match( /^\\/log-in(?:\\/([a-z]{2}))?\\/?$/ ) ) {
			var login = \'https://\'

			if ( matches[1] ) {
				login += matches[1] + \'.\';
			}

			login += \'wordpress.com/wp-login.php\';

			if ( window.location.search ) {
				login += window.location.search + \'&\';
			} else {
				login += \'?\';
			}
			login += \'no_calypso=1\';

			window.location = login;
		} else {
			window.location = \'https://wordpress.com/browsehappy?url=\' + encodeURIComponent( window.location );
		}
	}
})();

id="secondary" class="layout__secondary" data-reactid="70"></div></div></div></div><script>(function() {
	function isSupported() {
		var ios, version, ua, android, matches;

		ua = window.navigator.userAgent;

		if ( ! window.history ||
				! window.history.pushState ||
				! window.history.replaceState ||
				! ( '__proto__' in Object.prototype )
		) {
			return false;
		}

		function getFirstMatch( regex ) {
			var match = ua.match( regex );
			return ( match && match.length > 1 && match[1] ) || '';
		}

		ios = getFirstMatch( /(ipod|iphone|ipad)/i ).toLowerCase();
		version = getFirstMatch( /version\/(\d+(\.\d+)? )/i );

		if ( ios && version < 6 ) {
			// disable for now because it is breaking Chrome on iOS
			//return false;
		}

		android = getFirstMatch( /android (\d+)/i );
		if ( android && android < 3 ) {
			return false;
		}

		return true;
	}

	if ( ! isSupported() ) {
		if ( matches = window.location.pathname.match( /^\/log-in(?:\/([a-z]{2}))?\/?$/ ) ) {
			var login = 'https://'

			if ( matches[1] ) {
				login += matches[1] + '.';
			}

			login += 'wordpress.com/wp-login.php';

			if ( window.location.search ) {
				login += window.location.search + '&';
			} else {
				login += '?';
			}
			login += 'no_calypso=1';

			window.location = login;
		} else {
			window.location = 'https://wordpress.com/browsehappy?url=' + encodeURIComponent( window.location );
		}
	}
})();

			"%cWait! This browser feature runs code that can alter your website or its security, " +
			"and is intended for developers. If you've been told to copy and paste something here " +
			"to enable a feature, someone may be trying to compromise your account. Please make " +
			"sure you understand the code and trust the source before adding anything here.",
			"font-size:large;"
		);
	}
